GULF COASTS OF THE UNITED STATES. ADJUSTING FOR THE SALE OF MENDOTA FOR BOTH YEARS, NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN THE HOMEOWNERS AND OTHER LINE OF BUSINESS IN 2007 INCREASED 7% OVER 2006.

