HAVE NOT BEEN ADJUSTED TO REFLECT THE TIME VALUE OF MONEY. ACCORDINGLY, THE AMOUNTS ABOVE WILL DIFFER FROM THE COMPANY'S BALANCE SHEET TO THE EXTENT THAT DEPOSIT VALUES IN THE BALANCE SHEET HAVE BEEN

DISCOUNTED USING DEPOSIT ACCOUNTING.

