THE

$2.98 BILLION DECLINE IN GROSS CLAIMS AND CLAIM ADJUSTMENT EXPENSE RESERVES SINCE DECEMBER 31, 2007 PRIMARILY REFLECTED FAVORABLE PRIOR YEAR RESERVE DEVELOPMENT DURING

