NET FAVORABLE PRIOR YEAR RESERVE DEVELOPMENT TOTALED $21 MILLION IN 2006, PRIMARILY CONCENTRATED IN THE

COMMERCIAL

MULTI-PERIL, GENERAL LIABILITY, PROPERTY AND COMMERCIAL AUTOMOBILE LINES OF BUSINESS, PARTIALLY OFFSET BY INCREASES FOR ASBESTOS RESERVES AND ENVIRONMENTAL RESERVES (AS DISCUSSED IN MORE DETAIL IN THE

