THE

COMPANY'S AMENDED AND RESTATED 2004 STOCK INCENTIVE PLAN, THE LEGACY SPC 1994 STOCK INCENTIVES PLAN AND THE LEGACY TPC 2002 INCENTIVE PLAN PROVIDE SETTLEMENT ALTERNATIVES TO

EMPLOYEES IN WHICH THE COMPANY REPURCHASES SHARES TO COVER TAX WITHHOLDING COSTS AND EXERCISE COSTS. DURING THE YEARS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2008 AND 2007, THE COMPANY PURCHASED $38 MILLION

